b9abda93-d643-4d65-afef-8dfd7cf74b85	8e31ade8-3c27-4e3e-bb5f-c763fe6d6a2b	Hello sir, good morning. We are calling from OnePlug EV. Sir, you have installed the OnePlug EV charger, but it is not being used. Could you explain the reason for this? Sir, there seems to be a problem with the AC charger at the station. No sir, the car has been sold. I only have a two-wheeler now. Can I use the charger for a two-wheeler now? No sir, the charger is not compatible with two-wheelers. Alright, I no longer own an EV car. If I purchase another EV, I could use the charger again. Ok sir, thank you.	ta	99	42.54	[{"start": 3.1, "end": 6.1, "text": "Hello sir, good morning. We are calling from OnePlug EV."}, {"start": 13.1, "end": 17.1, "text": "Sir, you have installed the OnePlug EV charger, but it is not being used."}, {"start": 17.1, "end": 19.1, "text": "Could you explain the reason for this?"}, {"start": 19.1, "end": 23.1, "text": "Sir, there seems to be a problem with the AC charger at the station."}, {"start": 23.1, "end": 28.1, "text": "No sir, the car has been sold. I only have a two-wheeler now."}, {"start": 28.1, "end": 30.1, "text": "Can I use the charger for a two-wheeler now?"}, {"start": 30.1, "end": 32.1, "text": "No sir, the charger is not compatible with two-wheelers."}, {"start": 32.1, "end": 37.1, "text": "Alright, I no longer own an EV car. If I purchase another EV, I could use the charger again."}, {"start": 37.1, "end": 39.1, "text": "Ok sir, thank you."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "An agent from OnePlug EV contacted a customer to inquire about the underutilization of their installed charger. The customer explained they sold their EV car and now use a two-wheeler, which is incompatible with the charger.", "main_concern": "Inquire about the underutilization of an installed charger.", "outcome": "The customer clarified the charger is unused due to selling their EV car.", "action_needed": "None", "what_happened": "An agent from OnePlug EV called the customer regarding their charger that had been installed but was not being used. The customer explained the EV car had been sold and they now only own a two-wheeler, which is incompatible with the charger. The conversation ended amicably with no further action required.", "issue_detected": false, "issue_type": null, "severity": null, "all_issues": [], "sentiment": "Neutral", "sentiment_score": 0.0}	2026-06-26 04:10:51.582414	2026-06-26 04:10:51.58242
41112c9f-9a6a-4e05-99f2-53781759bbbd	2bbf6260-87e7-4371-a57e-1792f64daf05	Have you contacted OnePlug EV? OnePlug EV car charging station. Have you installed our mobile application? I haven't done any charging yet. Is it difficult for you to use the app? The EV belongs to another family. I haven't used it for charging. Alright, thank you.	ta	46	36.88	[{"start": 2.53, "end": 4.53, "text": "Have you contacted OnePlug EV?"}, {"start": 10.53, "end": 12.53, "text": "OnePlug EV car charging station."}, {"start": 14.53, "end": 16.53, "text": "Have you installed our mobile application?"}, {"start": 16.53, "end": 18.53, "text": "I haven't done any charging yet."}, {"start": 18.53, "end": 22.53, "text": "Is it difficult for you to use the app?"}, {"start": 24.53, "end": 28.53, "text": "The EV belongs to another family. I haven't used it for charging."}, {"start": 30.53, "end": 32.53, "text": "Alright, thank you."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "A customer clarified they had installed the OnePlug EV app but had not used it for charging, as the EV belonged to another family.", "main_concern": "Clarification on app usage and EV ownership.", "outcome": "The agent confirmed the situation, and the discussion concluded without any issue.", "action_needed": "None", "what_happened": "A customer responded to the agent's inquiry about their OnePlug EV app usage. They confirmed the app was installed but clarified they had not used it for charging because the EV belonged to another family. The agent acknowledged this and concluded the call politely.", "issue_detected": false, "issue_type": null, "severity": null, "all_issues": [], "sentiment": "Neutral", "sentiment_score": 0.0}	2026-06-26 04:11:13.027611	2026-06-26 04:11:13.027616
