 discuss their EV charging stations and encourage future service usage.", "main_concern": "Customer was contacted to inquire why they haven't used the OnePlug EV service after installing the app.", "outcome": "The agent provided information about the locations of charging stations and encouraged the customer to use the service in the future.", "action_needed": "None", "what_happened": "An agent from OnePlug EV made an outbound call to a customer who had installed the OnePlug EV app but hadn't used the charging service. The customer inquired about the locations of charging stations, and the agent explained their availability in Tamil Nadu and Kerala. The customer stated they might not have been aware of the stations and acknowledged they hadn't used the app. The agent concluded by encouraging the customer to consider using the charging service in the future.", "issue_detected": false, "issue_type": null, "severity": null, "all_issues": [], "sentiment": "Neutral", "sentiment_score": 0.0}	2026-06-26 04:41:39.024734	2026-06-26 04:41:39.024739
