 station is showing 6 kilometers away."}, {"start": 107.9, "end": 113.9, "text": "Could you send us the live location for the nearest working charger? I will share my phone number via WhatsApp."}, {"start": 113.9, "end": 116.9, "text": "I will send you the station location on WhatsApp."}, {"start": 116.9, "end": 118.9, "text": "Can I send it to the same number?"}, {"start": 118.9, "end": 120.9, "text": "Okay, sir."}, {"start": 121.9, "end": 122.9, "text": "Thank you, brother."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "A customer called to find the nearest working EV charging station as their car had shut down near Dharmapuri toll. The agent assisted by providing the live location via WhatsApp.", "main_concern": "Finding a nearby working EV charging station.", "outcome": "The agent shared the live location of the nearest charging station with the customer via WhatsApp.", "action_needed": "None", "what_happened": "A customer called OnePlug EV support regarding the need for a nearby charging station as their car had shut down near the Dharmapuri toll. They mentioned that the Tata Power charging station at Nallampalli Indian Oil Petrol Pump was under maintenance. The agent confirmed the location of another charging station about 5.5 kilometers away and sent its live location to the customer via WhatsApp.", "issue_detected": true, "issue_type": "Technical Issue", "severity": "Medium", "all_issues": [{"issue_type": "Technical Issue", "severity": "Medium"}], "sentiment": "Neutral", "sentiment_score": 0.0}	2026-06-26 07:28:16.117585	2026-06-26 07:28:16.11759
