.08, "end": 49.08, "text": "Not really. It seems to be available more in specific regions."}, {"start": 61.36, "end": 67.36, "text": "I only found one charging station location in Palakkad."}, {"start": 67.36, "end": 74.36, "text": "Yes, currently our station is only in Palakkad. We plan to expand across Tamil Nadu in the future."}, {"start": 74.36, "end": 79.36, "text": "Alright. What setup charges are involved for these expansions?"}, {"start": 86.36, "end": 92.36, "text": "Are you interested in our technology offerings?"}, {"start": 92.36, "end": 96.36, "text": "I am not fully aware, but I am open to learning about it."}, {"start": 96.36, "end": 103.36, "text": "I will share your details with the marketing team, and they will contact you to explain the technology in detail."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "The agent called a customer to gather feedback on the OnePlug EV charging experience and discussed future plans for expansion. The customer expressed overall satisfaction and openness to learning about new technology offerings.", "main_concern": "Feedback on charging experience and availability of stations in frequent travel areas.", "outcome": "The customer was satisfied with the service, and their details will be shared with the marketing team for further contact regarding technology offerings.", "action_needed": "Share customer details with the marketing team for further outreach.", "what_happened": "An agent from OnePlug EV contacted a customer to obtain feedback on their recent charging experience at a OnePlug charging station. The customer confirmed satisfaction with the service and found it more convenient than other providers but noted limited availability of charging stations in frequent travel areas, mentioning Palakkad as one of the locations. The conversation shifted to discussing potential setup charges for future expansions, and the agent offered to have the marketing team reach out to the customer to provide details about innovative tech