.32, "end": 55.52, "text": "Your station charges \\u20b922 or \\u20b924 plus tax, which is very high. It's a very bad experience."}, {"start": 59.84, "end": 67.36, "text": "In Kerala, electricity prices are very low compared to your station."}, {"start": 71.76, "end": 76.0, "text": "I am from Kerala, and I feel your charging costs are too high compared to the stations there."}, {"start": 76.88, "end": 81.92, "text": "I am dissatisfied as your pricing is \\u20b96 to \\u20b97 higher than expected."}, {"start": 89.84, "end": 95.6, "text": "Please take my suggestions into consideration and inform your management."}, {"start": 95.6, "end": 104.16, "text": "I come to Tamil Nadu weekly, and I charge my new car one or two times during each visit."}, {"start": 104.16, "end": 111.12, "text": "On average, I use Tamil Nadu charging stations six to seven times a week, but I'm very unhappy with the pricing."}, {"start": 117.6, "end": 117.92, "text": "Thank you."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "A customer expressed dissatisfaction with high energy consumption costs at the OnePlug EV charging station in Madukarai compared to other charging stations in Kerala and Indian Oil pumps.", "main_concern": "High energy consumption costs at the Madukarai charging station.", "outcome": "The agent noted the feedback and promised to relay it to management.", "action_needed": "Review pricing at the Madukarai charging station; consider aligning costs with competitors.", "what_happened": "An agent from OnePlug EV called a customer to collect feedback for a charging session at the Madukarai station. The customer expressed dissatisfaction with high energy consumption costs at the station compared to other chargers in Kerala and at Indian Oil stations, stating that \\u20b922 plus tax was excessive. The customer requested that this feedback be forwarded to management and shared that they regularly use charging stations in Tamil Nadu. The agent acknowledged the feedback and assured it would be