"Yes, it was 27 kilowatts for my car model, the MG ZS EV Pro."}, {"start": 119.56, "end": 123.72, "text": "At what percentage did you initiate charging at the second station, sir?"}, {"start": 123.72, "end": 130.6, "text": "At the second station, around 41% or nearly 50%."}, {"start": 130.6, "end": 142.6, "text": "Okay, sorry for the inconvenience. Usually, you can get up to around 45kW at that station."}, {"start": 142.6, "end": 146.6, "text": "Yes, that was my expectation, but unfortunately, I don't know what caused the limitation."}, {"start": 146.6, "end": 152.6, "text": "It only gave me around 27 kilowatts specifically during that session."}, {"start": 152.6, "end": 155.6, "text": "That is my only improvement suggestion."}, {"start": 155.6, "end": 157.6, "text": "Apart from that, the service is really good."}, {"start": 157.6, "end": 162.32, "text": "The location is also very convenient, just near the toll gate, so it is easily accessible."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "The customer shared feedback about their recent charging experience at two stations and suggested improvements regarding charging speed at one of the stations.", "main_concern": "The customer expressed concerns about slower charging speeds at the second station and suggested improving the charging efficiency.", "outcome": "The customer provided feedback and specifically highlighted areas of improvement for charging speed at one station. The agent acknowledged the concerns and apologized for the inconvenience.", "action_needed": "Investigate the charging speed limitation at the second station and ensure optimal performance for future sessions.", "what_happened": "The agent from OnePlug EV called a customer who had recently used two EV charging stations: Arasan Bakery and Salai Puthup 12 Plus in Madurai. The customer shared positive feedback about the fast charging at the first station with a 128kW charger but noted slower speeds at the second station with a 30kW charger, where charging