els near your land?"}, {"start": 252.66, "end": 260.42, "text": "We are planning to install a refreshment area, possibly a coffee shop."}, {"start": 260.42, "end": 280.46, "text": "What is the size of the land where the charger will be installed?"}, {"start": 283.42, "end": 293.86, "text": "It is about 410 square feet. It can accommodate 5 to 6 cars."}, {"start": 344.02, "end": 354.88, "text": "Do you prefer an AC or DC charger?"}, {"start": 354.88, "end": 366.82, "text": "I prefer the faster option, which is DC. Perhaps a 60-kilowatt option."}, {"start": 366.82, "end": 373.34, "text": "Our marketing team will explain all the details and guide you on the next steps."}, {"start": 373.34, "end": 387.34, "text": "How soon can you begin the initial setup?"}, {"start": 387.34, "end": 395.9, "text": "We can start within one month. I heard about your brand recently."}, {"start": 395.9, "end": 404.86, "text": "Thank you. Our marketing team will reach out to you within 24 hours."}, {"start": 404.86, "end": 410.38, "text": "Thank you. Have a great day."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "An agent from OnePlug EV called the customer to collect details about their franchise application. Information regarding land size, location, charger type, and setup timeline was confirmed.", "main_concern": "Franchise application and charger installation setup.", "outcome": "The agent collected installation details and informed the customer the marketing team would contact them within 24 hours.", "action_needed": "Marketing team needs to follow up with the customer within 24 hours.", "what_happened": "A representative from OnePlug EV called a customer who had submitted a franchise application to clarify details about their proposal. The customer provided information about the location of the charger (Rawalapalayam, near NH216), the residential address in Ongole, and the land specifications. The customer confirmed interest in setting up a charger and preferred a DC charger (60-kilowatt 