, "end": 272.74, "text": "Yes, correct. Absolutely."}, {"start": 272.74, "end": 292.74, "text": "Alright, sir. Is this an immediate proposal within the next three months or in 1-2 months?"}, {"start": 297.74, "end": 310.74, "text": "Do you have any ideas regarding what type of machine you would like to install, sir?"}, {"start": 314.74, "end": 328.74, "text": "If it's fast charging, we offer machines with capacities of 30kW, 60kW, 90kW, 120kW, and 180kW. Which would you prefer?"}, {"start": 328.74, "end": 332.74, "text": "I will note down 60kW."}, {"start": 336.74, "end": 338.74, "text": "Our team will contact you shortly with more details."}, {"start": 352.74, "end": 369.74, "text": "Regarding location, Kangeyam to Karur is approximately 50 km. Somewhere in between would be ideal for the installation."}, {"start": 380.74, "end": 382.74, "text": "Thank you so much for your time."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "An agent from OnePlug EV contacted a customer to discuss his usage of their app and the installation of EV charging stations. The customer shared his travel preferences and expressed interest in installing a 60kW fast charging machine, suggesting potential locations.", "main_concern": "Inquiry about installing a fast EV charger and locations for charging stations.", "outcome": "The agent noted the customer's details and informed him that the marketing team would reach out with further information regarding installation and business collaboration.", "action_needed": "Follow up with the customer to provide further details and finalize installation plans.", "what_happened": "An agent from OnePlug EV called a customer to discuss his usage of the OnePlug EV app and the reasons for not utilizing their charging services despite downloading the app. After exploring charging station locations in Coimbatore, Tiruppur, and nearby regions, the agent assisted the customer with details on installing charging machines. The customer expressed interest in installing 