sk why?"}, {"start": 43.0, "end": 48.0, "text": "There's an issue, madam. My car is not charging, and I have already filed a complaint."}, {"start": 48.0, "end": 51.0, "text": "What is your car model, sir?"}, {"start": 51.0, "end": 53.56, "text": "My car is a Tata Nexon EV, madam."}, {"start": 54.16, "end": 55.56, "text": "What is the charger type you are using, sir?"}, {"start": 81.0, "end": 84.5, "text": "There is an issue with the Exicom charger, madam. It is not working properly."}, {"start": 90.5, "end": 97.5, "text": "Sir, where did you last try to charge using the Exicom charger?"}, {"start": 97.5, "end": 99.5, "text": "At Dara Hotel and Aishwarya Hotel."}, {"start": 99.5, "end": 103.5, "text": "Ok, sir. There was some power issue at that time, which may have caused the problem."}, {"start": 106.5, "end": 109.5, "text": "The issue seems to be with the charger provided, madam\\u2014it's an Exicom charger issue."}, {"start": 143.5, "end": 146.5, "text": "Sir, you're saying the issue is with the charger hardware, not the application side?"}, {"start": 157.5, "end": 160.5, "text": "I didn't say there was any problem with the OnePlug EV app, madam."}, {"start": 162.5, "end": 166.82, "text": "There seem to be issues with the charger firmware and electronic mismatches."}, {"start": 276.66, "end": 278.66, "text": "You pay Rs.7.90 to the government."}, {"start": 324.66, "end": 327.66, "text": "There are known issues with the hardware and Exicom chargers. Sometimes, it is not compatible with some EVs."}, {"start": 343.66, "end": 345.66, "text": "Ok sir."}, {"start": 345.66, "end": 347.66, "text": "Thank you."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "An agent from OnePlug EV reached out to the customer regarding issues with charging a Tata Nexon EV using an Exicom charger. The customer reported a previous complaint due to charger malfunctioning and discussed high charging costs.", "main_concern": "Faulty Exicom charger and high charging costs.", "outcome": "Customer inf