 "end": 92.0, "text": "How much charge does your car currently have, ma'am?"}, {"start": 92.0, "end": 94.0, "text": "22%."}, {"start": 94.0, "end": 96.0, "text": "I now have 43%."}, {"start": 96.0, "end": 102.0, "text": "If the charge is below 20% or above 80%, the charging speed is slower."}, {"start": 102.0, "end": 112.0, "text": "Once it gets closer to 30%, the speed increases. This is common behavior across all cars."}, {"start": 116.0, "end": 118.0, "text": "Are you the only customer charging right now?"}, {"start": 120.0, "end": 122.0, "text": "Yes, I am the only one charging."}, {"start": 122.0, "end": 124.0, "text": "Which model is your car, ma'am?"}, {"start": 126.0, "end": 128.0, "text": "Tata Nexon EV."}, {"start": 128.0, "end": 130.0, "text": "Okay, you're using a Tata Nexon EV."}, {"start": 134.0, "end": 136.0, "text": "If more than one car is connected, the power splits. But since you're alone, you'll get full speed."}, {"start": 142.0, "end": 150.0, "text": "Okay ma'am, if there's any issue, please contact customer care. We're always here to support you."}, {"start": 150.0, "end": 155.0, "text": "Is your OnePlug EV app logged in, ma'am?"}, {"start": 160.0, "end": 165.0, "text": "Yes, I have logged in. How can I check the charging status?"}, {"start": 165.0, "end": 173.0, "text": "In the OnePlug EV app, you can check the charging percentage on the home page."}, {"start": 173.0, "end": 176.0, "text": "Select the 'Home' option, and it will show you the details."}, {"start": 176.0, "end": 181.0, "text": "At the bottom of the app, you'll find the options 'Home' and 'Profile'."}, {"start": 181.0, "end": 185.0, "text": "My wallet balance is showing zero now. Why is that happening?"}, {"start": 189.0, "end": 191.7, "text": "Are you using the OnePlug EV app right now?"}, {"start": 191.7, "end": 194.84, "text": "Yes, the charge is increasing now. I see it going up to 25%."}, {"start": 205.38, "end": 208.12, "text": "If the wallet balance is zero, the session ma