ir. I will inform our backend team about this concern."}, {"start": 46.94, "end": 48.94, "text": "May I know your car model, sir?"}, {"start": 48.94, "end": 50.94, "text": "It's the MG ZS EV."}, {"start": 56.94, "end": 65.26, "text": "Do you have any suggestions for improving our station, sir?"}, {"start": 65.26, "end": 73.86, "text": "Yes. You need to add more charging points, at least two or three guns. Having just one is not enough."}, {"start": 73.86, "end": 82.54, "text": "One gun is insufficient, especially considering the demand. For example, there were eight cars in a queue when I visited."}, {"start": 82.54, "end": 87.42, "text": "It's difficult for users if there\\u2019s only one gun. You should consider setting up stations with more guns in other locations as well."}, {"start": 88.54, "end": 95.1, "text": "Overall, the station was quick and effective, but more charging points need to be added."}, {"start": 95.1, "end": 101.74, "text": "That's the only major improvement needed."}, {"start": 111.9, "end": 115.9, "text": "Otherwise, the charging was very fast and convenient."}, {"start": 115.9, "end": 119.02, "text": "Reducing the unit cost and improving station capacity would make things better."}, {"start": 119.02, "end": 127.1, "text": "Okay. Thank you for your feedback, sir."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "The customer provided feedback on their charging session at the MRC Nagar station, highlighting high unit costs and insufficient charging guns at the station.", "main_concern": "The customer raised concerns about high energy costs and insufficient charging points at the MRC Nagar station.", "outcome": "The agent noted the customer's feedback on energy costs and station capacity to relay it to the backend team.", "action_needed": "The backend team needs to evaluate reducing unit costs and adding more charging guns at the MRC Nagar station.", "what_happened": "An agent from OnePlug EV called a customer to discuss their experience with the charg