!	ta	318	715.4	[{"start": 0.0, "end": 7.0, "text": "Hello sir, good evening. This is Ganesh calling from OnePlug EV."}, {"start": 7.0, "end": 9.0, "text": "Good evening, tell me."}, {"start": 9.0, "end": 14.0, "text": "Sir, we noticed that you've filled out a franchise inquiry form showing interest. We'll call you once we finalize the details."}, {"start": 14.0, "end": 20.0, "text": "Can we confirm your name, email ID, mobile number, and residential details?"}, {"start": 20.0, "end": 25.0, "text": "Yes, my residential address is Chennai, number 35, VR Garden Street, Patalam, PIN code 600012."}, {"start": 25.0, "end": 33.0, "text": "You have mentioned your property is near SR Petrol Bunk, correct? Are you planning to proceed with that location or another one?"}, {"start": 33.0, "end": 37.0, "text": "Yes, I plan to proceed with that location."}, {"start": 37.0, "end": 58.0, "text": "We will set up DC fast chargers at the location. Could you share the size of your property and confirm other details?"}, {"start": 58.0, "end": 75.0, "text": "It is 16 cents in size with 23 meters frontage and 30 meters depth. Currently, there is a petrol pump and tank that can be removed to set up EV chargers."}, {"start": 75.0, "end": 84.5, "text": "Based on your budget of 8-10 lakhs, you can start with 30kW chargers and choose upgradeable or non-upgradeable models."}, {"start": 84.5, "end": 97.5, "text": "For example, 60kW chargers are upgradeable to 90kW or 120kW models. The setup cost will range from 16-21.5 lakhs, depending on specifications and components covered."}, {"start": 97.5, "end": 110.5, "text": "All costs include EB connections, setup, and civil work. If you're comfortable, the marketing team will meet you to proceed further."}, {"start": 110.5, "end": 138.5, "text": "Regarding return on investment, a percentage of the revenue generated at the station will be your share. Full details will be shared later by the marketing representative."}, {"start": 138.5, "end": 151.5, "t