tiated within 1 minute and 30 seconds of setting it up. If not, the connection will fail. Because the charger gun will automatically time out. Yes, sir. Okay, sir. I will try again next time. What is your name, madam? Sumitra. Sumitra, okay. Do you have five of us? Sir, the head office is in Thirupuram. Thirupuram? Yes, uncle. Oh, okay. Thank you.	ta	410	184	[{"start": 0.0, "end": 2.0, "text": "Hello."}, {"start": 2.0, "end": 4.0, "text": "Hello, tell me."}, {"start": 4.0, "end": 7.0, "text": "Good evening, sir. I am calling from OnePlug EV."}, {"start": 7.0, "end": 8.0, "text": "Hello."}, {"start": 8.0, "end": 11.0, "text": "This is about the OnePlug EV charging station, sir."}, {"start": 13.0, "end": 14.0, "text": "Hello."}, {"start": 15.0, "end": 19.0, "text": "Sir, we are calling from the OnePlug EV car charging station."}, {"start": 19.0, "end": 21.0, "text": "Where are you located?"}, {"start": 21.0, "end": 25.0, "text": "OnePlug EV car charging station, sir."}, {"start": 25.0, "end": 27.0, "text": "Okay."}, {"start": 27.0, "end": 33.0, "text": "You have installed the OnePlug EV app, sir, but your car is not charging. Could you explain the issue?"}, {"start": 35.0, "end": 36.0, "text": "Is that so?"}, {"start": 36.0, "end": 37.0, "text": "Yes, sir."}, {"start": 37.0, "end": 42.0, "text": "It is through OnePlug, right? Where is the Madurai-Pollachi bypass located?"}, {"start": 42.0, "end": 46.0, "text": "Madurai is at the Vandiyar toll gate, sir."}, {"start": 46.0, "end": 49.0, "text": "That is near the Pollachi bypass, correct?"}, {"start": 49.0, "end": 51.0, "text": "Yes, sir. That is correct."}, {"start": 51.0, "end": 56.0, "text": "A demo vehicle was brought here, but the car was returned afterward."}, {"start": 56.0, "end": 61.0, "text": "We tried to charge it, but it didn't work."}, {"start": 61.0, "end": 65.0, "text": "Okay. Did you speak with customer care regarding this issue?"}, {"start": 65.0, "end": 68.0, "text": "No, we did not speak to customer care."}, {"start": 68.0, "end": 73.0, "text": "We called them earlier and asked them to get the vehicle to us as soon as possible."}, {"start": 73.0, "end": 74.0, "text": "Okay."}, {"start": 74.0, "end": 81.0, "text": "That\\u2019s why we decided not to recharge with OnePlug and returned the car."}, {"start": 81.0, "end": 83.0, "text": "Okay, thank you."}, {"start": 83.0, "end": 90.0, "text": "Okay, sir. If you face any other issues, please call customer care, and we will assist you."}, {"start": 90.0, "end": 91.0, "text": "Is that so?"}, {"start": 91.0, "end": 92.0, "text": "Yes."}, {"start": 92.0, "end": 94.0, "text": "What is the customer care number?"}, {"start": 94.0, "end": 98.0, "text": "The number is available on the notice board and also on the machine."}, {"start": 98.0, "end": 103.0, "text": "Sir, why is the charging machine not working? What is the reason?"}, {"start": 103.0, "end": 106.0, "text": "It might be due to a timeout issue with the charger gun, sir."}, {"start": 106.0, "end": 110.0, "text": "If the machine is turned off, the current flow will stop, sir."}, {"start": 110.0, "end": 113.0, "text": "No, the current is on. I am giving you the information as it is."}, {"start": 113.0, "end": 117.0, "text": "The current is on, but the charger gun got disconnected during rotation."}, {"start": 117.0, "end": 120.0, "text": "The connector needle is not properly engaged."}, {"start": 120.0, "end": 126.0, "text": "Even after recharging, the operation is not successful."}, {"start": 126.0, "end": 128.0, "text": "It doesn't work at all."}, {"start": 128.0, "end": 132.0, "text": "You can retry recharging and check with the OnePlug EV app."}, {"start": 132.0, "end": 137.0, "text": "I just installed the app for the first time."}, {"start": 137.0, "end": 143.0, "text": "If the charger gun times out, please call customer care about the issue."}, {"start": 143.0, "end": 146.0, "text": "The charger gun is functioning correctly."}, {"start": 146.0, "end": 150.0, "text": "Make sure the gun is fitted properly."}, {"start": 150.0, "end": 154.0, "text": "Short charging should be initiated within 1 minute and 30 seconds of setting it up."}, {"start": 154.0, "end": 158.0, "text": "If not, the connection will fail."}, {"start": 158.0, "end": 162.0, "text": "Because the charger gun will automatically time out. Yes, sir."}, {"start": 162.0, "end": 166.0, "text": "Okay, sir. I will try again next time."}, {"start": 166.0, "end": 168.0, "text": "What is your name, madam?"}, {"start": 168.0, "end": 170.0, "text": "Sumitra."}, {"start": 170.0, "end": 173.0, "text": "Sumitra, okay. Do you have five of us?"}, {"start": 173.0, "end": 175.0, "text": "Sir, the head office is in Thirupuram."}, {"start": 175.0, "end": 177.0, "text": "Thirupuram?"}, {"start": 177.0, "end": 179.0, "text": "Yes, uncle."}, {"start": 179.0, "end": 181.0, "text": "Oh, okay."}, {"start": 181.0, "end": 183.0, "text": "Thank you."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "An agent contacted a customer to address a failed charging issue at a OnePlug EV station, discussed probable causes, and provided assistance instructions.", "main_concern": "The agent contacted the customer about a car failing to charge at the OnePlug EV charging station.", "outcome": "The agent explained potential reasons for the issue and advised the customer to retry charging and contact customer care if needed.", "action_needed": "The customer should retry charging and ensure the charger gun is properly fitted within the recommended timeframe; contact customer care for further support if the problem persists.", "what_happened": "An agent called a customer to discuss a failed charging attempt at a OnePlug EV charging station. The customer revealed they had installed the OnePlug EV app and attempted charging but the session was unsuccessful. The agent suggested possible reasons, such as a timeout issue with the charger gun or improper device connections. They explained the need to fit the gun correctly and initiate charging within the required time window. The agent provided instructions to resolve the issue, advised contacting customer care if the problem continued, and concluded the call with an offer of assistance.", "issue_detected": true, "issue_type": "Technical Issue", "severity": "Medium", "all_issues": [{"issue_type": "Technical Issue", "severity": "Medium"}], "sentiment": "Neutral", "sentiment_score": 0.0}	2026-06-30 12:11:56.622644	2026-06-30 12:11:56.622651
