e handling franchise-related inquiries and identifying locations."}, {"start": 40.0, "end": 46.0, "text": "Sir, there are two categories of chargers, AC chargers and DC chargers."}, {"start": 46.0, "end": 51.0, "text": "For commercial purposes and fast charging, we recommend DC chargers."}, {"start": 54.0, "end": 58.0, "text": "The DC fast charging starts with 30 kW."}, {"start": 61.0, "end": 65.0, "text": "The approximate setup cost is around 10 lakhs."}, {"start": 68.0, "end": 71.0, "text": "Typically, one charger will have two plugs."}, {"start": 74.0, "end": 77.0, "text": "If a customer charges their vehicle from 0 to 100%, it will take about 1 hour and 45 minutes."}, {"start": 81.0, "end": 87.0, "text": "After that, chargers come in capacities like 30 kW, 60 kW, 90 kW, etc."}, {"start": 89.0, "end": 91.0, "text": "What is the current rate for charging?"}, {"start": 93.0, "end": 99.0, "text": "Charging rates depend on the area, time, and type of charger. It's not based on a fixed unit rate."}, {"start": 101.0, "end": 103.0, "text": "For charging within 45 minutes, the rate might be about Rs. 120 for 120 kW."}, {"start": 114.0, "end": 118.0, "text": "Because all the internal components of the machine will also vary, affecting pricing."}, {"start": 127.0, "end": 134.0, "text": "If you share your details, our marketing team will contact you within 24 hours to explain further."}, {"start": 137.0, "end": 139.0, "text": "Are you willing to share the details, sir?"}, {"start": 189.0, "end": 191.0, "text": "What is your email ID?"}, {"start": 217.0, "end": 219.0, "text": "The location is Peruntharayattu Kangayam Road."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "An agent from OnePlug EV called a customer to discuss unused registration, franchise opportunities, DC chargers, and charging specifications and costs.", "main_concern": "The agent called to inquire about the customer's inactivity following app registration and to provide details about chargers and franchises.", "o