ak Tamil?"}, {"start": 65.0, "end": 67.0, "text": "Yes, sir."}, {"start": 67.0, "end": 82.32, "text": "We have two plugs. When we use both to charge two cars, the charging stops."}, {"start": 82.32, "end": 87.52, "text": "This happened recently. This morning, we used one plug in Madurai."}, {"start": 87.52, "end": 93.28, "text": "Both cars showed the correct voltage."}, {"start": 93.28, "end": 98.68, "text": "But when we connected both cars, the charging stopped."}, {"start": 100.12, "end": 106.52, "text": "In the area near Kuzhendripetai, fast charging worked within 20 minutes."}, {"start": 108.92, "end": 111.04, "text": "Yes, it charged quickly in Kuzhendripetai."}, {"start": 111.04, "end": 121.04, "text": "But in Madurai, we used another car and another charger as the first setup stopped."}, {"start": 121.04, "end": 125.04, "text": "We had to restart charging 2-3 times."}, {"start": 133.04, "end": 139.04, "text": "We spent around \\u20b95000 using the charger. I still have \\u20b91000 in my wallet balance."}, {"start": 141.04, "end": 144.04, "text": "When we travel to Chennai, we plan to use this balance."}, {"start": 154.04, "end": 156.04, "text": "My car model is Tata Nexon EV."}, {"start": 160.04, "end": 162.04, "text": "Thank you."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "The agent called the customer to collect feedback about a charging station. The customer shared positive feedback about the charging speed but also highlighted an issue where the station stopped charging when two cars were plugged in simultaneously.", "main_concern": "The agent called the customer to ask for feedback on charging performance and station reliability.", "outcome": "The customer provided feedback, including a suggestion and positive remarks about fast charging performance. The agent acknowledged the feedback.", "action_needed": "Investigate and resolve the issue where charging stops when two cars are plugged in simultaneously.", "what_happened": "An outbound call was made by the