rt": 118.1, "end": 127.1, "text": "If costs are too high, people might return to petrol vehicles, even though EVs are more economical day to day."}, {"start": 127.1, "end": 129.1, "text": "Yes, sir."}, {"start": 129.1, "end": 135.1, "text": "If EV charging becomes slightly more affordable, it will encourage weekly EV usage over petrol."}, {"start": 135.1, "end": 142.86, "text": "Petrol expenses are significantly higher, like Rs.500 for a short-distance journey."}, {"start": 142.86, "end": 149.6, "text": "Whereas an EV charge for the same can last 3 hours and costs much less."}, {"start": 149.6, "end": 154.22, "text": "Petrol purchase takes 5 minutes, but EV provides long-term savings."}, {"start": 154.22, "end": 156.22, "text": "Okay, sir."}, {"start": 228.22, "end": 231.22, "text": "Thank you for your valuable feedback."}, {"start": 231.22, "end": 232.38, "text": "Have a great day, sir."}, {"start": 232.38, "end": 234.38, "text": "Thank you."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "The agent called the customer to gather feedback on their charging experience at Thoppur Coffee Stop. The customer appreciated the service but raised concerns about the high cost of charging and suggested reducing rates to attract more users.", "main_concern": "The agent called to obtain feedback on the charging experience and customer satisfaction.", "outcome": "The customer's feedback regarding high charging costs was noted and promised to be passed on to the appropriate team.", "action_needed": "Review pricing strategy based on customer feedback and consider adjustments to reduce charging costs.", "what_happened": "An agent from OnePlug EV called the customer to collect feedback on a recent charging session at Thoppur Coffee Stop. The customer found the service satisfactory but suggested reducing the charging rates, which they felt were high compared to other providers. The customer estimated that lower costs would attract additional users, enhancing profitability. The agent agreed t