xt": "Your name is Kittuswamy?"}, {"start": 73.0, "end": 76.0, "text": "Is your contact number 9629777309?"}, {"start": 79.0, "end": 81.0, "text": "How much battery percentage do you have in your car now?"}, {"start": 81.0, "end": 83.0, "text": "90%."}, {"start": 86.0, "end": 89.0, "text": "Okay ma'am, I'll call you back in a few minutes to stop."}, {"start": 92.0, "end": 93.0, "text": "Sure, thank you ma'am."}]	null	\N	{"analysed": true, "summary": "An agent from OnePlug EV contacted a customer to confirm the status of their charging process and assist with a network disconnection issue.", "main_concern": "An agent flagged a network disconnection issue with the charging machine and checked the customer's charging status.", "outcome": "The agent decided to call the customer back to assist with stopping the charging session and resolving the issue.", "action_needed": "The agent needs to follow up with the customer and ensure the charging session is stopped successfully and the network issue is addressed.", "what_happened": "An agent from OnePlug EV called the customer to check on the status of their charging machine. The customer confirmed their vehicle's charging progress but mentioned that the machine showed network unavailable and there was no option to stop the charging. The network had been working 15-20 minutes earlier but then got disconnected. Another user who attempted to connect was unsuccessful and left. The agent identified the need to follow up shortly to assist in stopping the charging session and resolving the network issue.", "issue_detected": true, "issue_type": "Technical Issue", "severity": "Medium", "all_issues": [{"issue_type": "Technical Issue", "severity": "Medium"}], "sentiment": "Neutral", "sentiment_score": 0.0}	2026-07-03 03:20:59.418415	2026-07-03 03:20:59.41842
